Singers are truly an extremely talented, awesome, & an equally they had sung beautifully this amazing Gujarati song Khalasi!!
👦👩🎶🎵🎧🎤😊😊❤️❤️
Thanks a lot @CokeStudioBharat for giving English translations of this amazing Gujarati song Khalasi!! 
So beautiful & enjoyable song!!
🇧🇩🇧🇩👩👩❤️❤️😊😊🎵🎶🎤🎧
